    <refsect1 xml:id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <varname>gl_InstanceID</varname> is a vertex language input variable that
            holds the integer index of the current primitive in an instanced draw
            command such as <function>glDrawArraysInstanced</function>. If the current
            primitive does not originate from an instanced draw command, the value
            of <varname>gl_InstanceID</varname> is zero.
        </para>
    </refsect1>
